95
00:08:11.810 --> 00:08:12.720
Ben Pfaff: Yes, have you been…

96
00:08:12.720 --> 00:08:13.750
Thorin (Joe): Another seven?

97
00:08:13.750 --> 00:08:15.070
Ben Pfaff: Have you been to the Exploratorium?

